<h2 class="bold font-l">Sun Wukong, The Monkey King</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
As Red states, Sun Wukong, The Monkey King, is the most beloved character from the whole of the Journey to The West, having been homaged and referenced throughout countless media. Which makes it a surprise to many, that he isn't actually the main protagonist of the text. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BreakoutCharacter" class='trope-example-link'>Breakout Character</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1f3m08" data-video-descrip="Buddha allows Sun Wukong to take the Jade Emperor's place, if he can successfully jump from his hand. However since Buddha is one with everything, Sun only gets as far as his fingers." data-video-title="Buddha's dare for Wukong" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1f3m08_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1f3m08.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ImpossibleTask" data-video-tropename="Impossible Task" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Literature/JourneyToTheWest,WebAnimation/OverlySarcasticProductions" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1f3m08.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Buddha's dare f...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="yn2n36" data-video-descrip="In his introductory chapters, Sun Wukong obtains not 1, not 2...but FIVE different methods of gaining immortality. This results in him being ageless, and practically unkillable." data-video-title="Son Wukong" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/yn2n36_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/yn2n36.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CompleteImmortality" data-video-tropename="Complete Immortality" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Literature/JourneyToTheWest,WebAnimation/OverlySarcasticProductions" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/yn2n36.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Son Wukong</span></p>
</a>
</div>
